{"type":"text","timestamp":1775838775398,"sessionID":"ses_287c383d3ffeG5DFOxm8iu0vtj","part":{"id":"prt_d783d3f48001U3N7maPzVMMH1h","messageID":"msg_d783d20940015vEuHIU3IBkWE0","sessionID":"ses_287c383d3ffeG5DFOxm8iu0vtj","type":"text","text":"Created proposal.md for AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 with:\n\n- **Purpose**: Define AgentRuntime CRD Go types for Kubernetes\n- **Module**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **Scope**: Spec/Status types, OpenAPI validation, required fields (maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, targetPort, podTemplate)\n- **Impact**: Workload Manager, client-go library, Helm chart, RBAC\n- **Design**: API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`, namespaced scope\n- **Alternatives**: Evaluated 3 options (separate API group, merged spec fields, v1 version) with rationale\n- **Implementation**: 4 phases over 2 days (types, validation, registration, codegen)\n- **Testing**: Unit tests + CRD validation\n- **References**: Kubernetes API conventions, Kubebuilder best practices, existing docs","time":{"start":1775838775397,"end":1775838775397}}}
